# Course notebooks (001_*.ipynb … ) — env vars they read.
#
# You normally do NOT need a local .env here: the Python code uses python-dotenv,
# which auto-discovers the .env at the REPO ROOT (it walks up the directory tree).
# Just set your key once in ../.env (repo root). This file only documents the vars.
#
# If you prefer a local .env anyway, copy this to ".env" in this folder.

ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-your-key-here

